18:55.476 --> 18:58.577
personal responsibility,
personal transformation.

18:58.578 --> 19:00.879
And it's helped me not be afraid

19:00.880 --> 19:02.583
to tell Graham what I need...

19:02.584 --> 19:05.118
um, including in bed.

19:05.119 --> 19:06.620
Which brings us to you.

19:06.621 --> 19:10.456
