before I enter her.

19:29.010 --> 19:32.211
And does she
physically stimulate you

19:32.212 --> 19:33.579
in any way prior to intercourse?

19:33.580 --> 19:35.049
There's no need.

19:35.050 --> 19:37.650
Once we begin, I'm--
I'm ready to go.

19:37.651 --> 19:40.520
A little too ready.

19:40.521 --> 19:42.555
And Margaret?

19:42.556 --> 19:44.558
It can take me a while.

19:44.559 --> 19:48.558
And Graham doesn't
satisfy you in other ways?

19:49.296 --> 19:51.998
He wants to. He tries to.

19:51.999 --> 19:54.901
But I want it to happen with us together,

19:54.902 --> 19:56.103
looking into each other's eyes.

19:58.105 --> 20:00.105
You think I've read too
many romance novels.

20:02.143 --> 20:06.579
Well, simultaneous
orgasm is a romantic notion,

20:06.580 --> 20:08.381
but it's not the norm.

20:08.382 --> 20:11.883
But it's happened for
us before, in the beginning.

20:11.884 --> 20:14.987
