have us ask ourselves.

20:30.572 --> 20:33.940
The only thing that matters
is right now.

20:33.941 --> 20:38.111
The past may hold some answers.

20:38.112 --> 20:40.980
Well, I've spent most of my life

20:40.981 --> 20:42.547
