20:42.548 --> 20:44.916
and a handful of girlfriends happy.

20:44.917 --> 20:46.451
And looking back on it now,

20:46.452 --> 20:48.422
I don't-- I don't even
think I liked them.

20:49.957 --> 20:52.258
But I-I like this one...

20:52.259 --> 20:55.462
because she doesn't want
to look backwards, either.

20:55.463 --> 20:59.565
Now, if you have some
practical advice to offer--

20:59.566 --> 21:00.900
