up on having it again.

21:42.509 --> 21:44.477
Uh, Dr. Scully!

21:44.478 --> 21:46.111
That's my name.
Don't wear it out.

21:46.112 --> 21:48.146
Oh, what are you
doing here on your day off?

21:48.147 --> 21:49.314
