21:49.315 --> 21:50.549
Oh, no, you're not.

21:50.550 --> 21:51.583
Uh, not in my book.

21:51.584 --> 21:53.554
And my book's the only one that counts.

21:53.555 --> 21:55.388
So scoot. Out.

21:55.389 --> 21:57.357
Barton.

21:59.093 --> 22:00.194
Margaret.

22:00.195 --> 22:02.428
Hello.

22:03.531 --> 22:06.966
