22:10.970 --> 22:11.970
So, what happens next?

22:11.971 --> 22:13.240
We-- we switch?

22:13.241 --> 22:15.608
Oh, I-I see.

22:15.609 --> 22:18.111
Uh...

22:18.112 --> 22:20.279
You must be...

22:20.280 --> 22:22.882
This is Graham Pennington.

22:22.883 --> 22:25.251
This is my husband, Barton Scully.

22:25.252 --> 22:26.985
- Oh, your ex-husband.
