24:02.617 --> 24:05.151
Why I insist on face-to-face sex...

24:05.152 --> 24:06.920
Why I can't do anything to him orally...

24:06.921 --> 24:09.488
Why I need him to see me, my body.

24:09.489 --> 24:10.989
Margaret, I understand your need

24:10.990 --> 24:12.359
